Install the latest version of Vim (Homebrew - OSX) and Solarized terminal first.

Installation:

    git clone git://github.com/brendonsoto/dotvim.git ~/.vim

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

Install plugins:

_On initial Vim launch_

    :PlugInstall
